Try an example
 
 
GOOGLEFINANCE(ticker, [attribute], [start_date], [end_date|num_days], [interval])
Example
GOOGLEFINANCE("GOOG", "price", "1/1/2014", "12/31/2014", "DAILY")
Summary
Fetches current or historical securities information from Google Finance.
ticker
The ticker symbol for the security to consider.
attribute - [optional]
The attribute to fetch about ticker from Google Finance.
start_date - [optional]
The start date when fetching historical data.
end_date|num_days - [optional]
The end date when fetching historical data, or the number of days from start_date for which to return data.
interval - [optional]
The frequency of returned data; either "DAILY" or "WEEKLY".
Learn more about GOOGLEFINANCE
